Item
2.02



Results of
Operations and Financial Condition




On
February 24, 2011, Hecla Mining Company (the “Company”)
issued a news release announcing the Company’s Fourth Quarter
2010 and twelve months ended December 31, 2010, financial
results.  The news release is attached hereto as Exhibit
99.1 to this Form 8-K.

In
accordance with General Instruction B.2 of Form 8-K, the
information in this Item 2.02, including Exhibit 99.1, shall not be
deemed to be “filed” for purposes of Section 18 of the
Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the “Exchange
Act”), or otherwise subject to the liability of that section,
and shall not be incorporated by reference into any registration
statement or other document filed under the Securities Act of 1933,
as amended, or the Exchange Act, except as shall be expressly set
forth by specific reference in such filing.

   

 




